Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you have been appointed as the new chief of the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept it respectfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You looks so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash your clothes, it'll disturb our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't get the dirt off, we will provide you a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not dirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Sami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't cry forever, Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}first and last{\i0} mission for you, as the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something decided by all the presbyters a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to sink the mud whale into the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,suicide in the sand, together with the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you can guide us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to death of proud, as the last chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your first and last mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must everybody die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who attacked us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,were from where used to be our mother country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ancestors were exiled to the sea of sand for their guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The exile is continued till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they have decided to execute us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those soldiers were intended
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to massacre all the people here in mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Their purpose is not invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way to avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody want to see our people be killed miserably
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For our pride, we shall go to that world ourselves elegantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Byakuroku-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our father... I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be sunk either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost himself for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Byakuroku-sama to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The eldest presbyter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you die unreasonably like Sami and Taisha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to die anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a way for everybody to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.00,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1266,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should ask our father, {\i1}Fallaina{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.66,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(764,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fallaina{\i0} knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fallaina? {\i0}The word the girl from that island said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean the mud whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me please, the eldest presbyter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean exactly by Fallaina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should restrain him in such a situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I supposed you have told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I should do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We told you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Strengthen the guard of the underground too, our Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he say something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to change our mood and proceed our task.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's start the preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don... Don't read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm not literate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want other read, don't scribble here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told by Tobikko,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that you succeeded in beating the enemy with your {\i1}thymia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you and Oni have succeeded
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in fighting back against those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you make it, {\i1}destroyer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Sami died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't fight back against somebody or beat somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't tell me that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you are scribbling your excuses on the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Samikko died,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you saved the kiddies of Tobikko, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your credit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be as easygoing as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me {\i1}you{\i0}, call me {\i1}Miss Ginshu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how I call you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important how you call me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,cuz it shows how you think about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach you how to use {\i1}thymia{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can fight against those guys when they come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, call me {\i1}Miss Ginshu{\i0} in respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss... Ginshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Chakuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucks, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, see you again, Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't climb from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you know why the world is so beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The souls of the people who have lived here so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are melted into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you can see it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami, you are alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be Chakuro's bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we {\i1}Shirushi{\i0} are short-lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we may become bedridden and die very soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's fine if you can be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a small wish like this can't be fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm no longer reluctant to leave this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Chakuro has a role to play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the recorder of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taisha-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The mud whale will be destroyed if you don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then nobody can know the truth of this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,since we will all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You must see everything with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It should not be the end of this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Should not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli, have you seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't you seen Sami and others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Suo and Lykos are suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are able to feel the hearts of people brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you think that is useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you don't connect everyone together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be our end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally found that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the presbyters is trying to sink the mud whale together with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo was opposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but he is arrested in the {\i1}internal area{\i0} now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to free a person's mind first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship which I was in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was intended to attack Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew nothing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told that this island is a hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was us who takes the hell here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to have so many emotions now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have seen your heart twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you, Lykos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Lykos,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be sunk into the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even control the destination of the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the presbytery know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the method to sink the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that nobody has ever entered in the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}internal area{\i0}! The underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though a few parts are used as the prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there are secret spaces where nobody can enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo is also arrested underground, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He also need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the useless arrows carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A week will soon be passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be prepared for their attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu! Lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gathering the weapons for hunting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sink the mud whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait a moment, it's a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are to go oppose the presbytery,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to fight against the vigilante group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The vigilante group?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think we can do it with these members?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicha,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's... Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooperate with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The mud whale is going to sink into the sea of sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been trapped in such a narrow island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finally found the would outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we are trampled by them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, there's nothing left in such an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, I care no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,An apatheia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's a prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we caught her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a soldier whose emotions have been taken away, and she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to treat guys without hearts as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever I do to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or abandoning this island like a dishcloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni, you are not telling your real heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fellows died,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and your dream and admiration for the world outside has been trashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand you feel hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can see your true heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,really willing to protect everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't find a way, this fact pains you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is trying to decide what should we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a decision without our own permissions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, you should give up him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put your time in dealing with that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody will be sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the vigilante group also guards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we know there's something underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, let's break it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo you are so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget I'm the man who ignored the scouts of the vigilante group!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm a little tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, there are more inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not familiar with the {\i1}thymia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate the young {\i1}Shirushi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that Chakky? How did you get that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ginshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Dear Miss Ginshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ginshu! This guy should...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We are ordered to prevent people from entering the underground by the presbytery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the reason of their order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I understand well is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My Chakky is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all for my cute Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Chakky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky, when did you get so familiar with the vigilante?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ginshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Misfortunes never come alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who are strong in their {\i1}thymia{\i0} can enter the vigilant group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's the top! The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.1 in the mud whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What's that... Disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine. We are facing the {\i1}internal area{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can no longer use {\i1}thymia{\i0}, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it's {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to help those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not somebody like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} are a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you go~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to pass here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly it becomes quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we are facing the no-entry area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should Suo be arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu and I will go around the prison and look for Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo has become our important chief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can you get him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Made by the workshop, used to destroy the lock of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell are you guys making!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbyters should be in the no-entry area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go ahead and investigate it. Join us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the method to sink the mud whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought us here but you don't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you have already known it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have touched that... at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The light...
